Common files and scripts for building Fedora documentation.

Assumptions: DocBook xml, *nix, en-US source language.

Extended by: Joshua Wulf <jwulf@fedoraproject.org>

This version of the brand enables video to display in both Google Chrome and Firefox using whatever codecs are present on the system.
It also enables a book to be consumed by the FUDCon Docs Hack System.
